CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 18, 1961, pg. 19 reads: Swing Your Partner - Loendi Club took on the air of an old-fashioned barn recently when the Loendi Ladies Auxlliary [sic] sponsored a square dance in club's parlors...-Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Seven women, including one second from right wearing plaid skirt and light colored blouse, clapping while square dancing in Loendi Club sponsored by the Loendi Ladies Auxiliary
